WEBVTT

01:37.120 --> 01:40.940
[The Best Thing]

01:41.330 --> 01:48.759
[Episode 19: Magnolia Buds]
[Spicy in taste and warm in nature.]
[They are associated with the lung and stomach meridians and help treat colds and nasal congestion.]

01:50.509 --> 01:52.509
What do you want to do tomorrow night?

01:52.950 --> 01:56.500
I want to go eat something delicious with you.

01:56.520 --> 01:59.330
Alright, I'll pick you up after work.

01:59.360 --> 01:59.910
No need.

01:59.930 --> 02:01.150
I can come back on my own.

02:01.290 --> 02:02.370
How?

02:02.430 --> 02:03.460
I'll take the bus.

02:03.480 --> 02:04.370
It's really convenient.

02:06.000 --> 02:06.590
Alright then.

02:06.870 --> 02:07.900
I'll wait for you at the bus stop.

02:07.950 --> 02:10.110
Okay, see you at the bus stop tomorrow.

02:17.460 --> 02:18.180
Here we are.

02:22.820 --> 02:23.940
Here, take this.

02:36.090 --> 02:36.810
What's wrong?

02:45.040 --> 02:46.000
He Suye.

02:48.010 --> 02:49.490
When I like someone,

02:51.630 --> 02:53.360
I like them for a very, very long time.

03:02.240 --> 03:02.870
What a coincidence.

03:04.060 --> 03:04.870
Me too.

03:22.760 --> 03:23.530
Good night.

03:24.400 --> 03:25.120
Good night.

03:32.590 --> 03:33.120
Bye.

04:10.690 --> 04:14.930
♫Two little hearts♫

04:15.930 --> 04:20.690
♫Found each other♫

04:24.280 --> 04:28.520
♫Never apart♫

04:27.430 --> 04:28.240
He Suye.

04:29.020 --> 04:33.620
♫Sticking together♫

04:29.040 --> 04:30.040
I like you.

04:32.240 --> 04:34.000
If you're still willing...

04:36.070 --> 04:37.390
would you be my boyfriend?

04:37.140 --> 04:42.040
♫You and I♫

04:43.320 --> 04:47.990
♫Side by side by side♫

04:50.140 --> 04:54.900
♫You and I♫

04:56.150 --> 04:58.460
♫Tonight♫

05:01.570 --> 05:07.360
♫And we go lalala♫

06:36.409 --> 06:37.060
Good morning.

06:46.940 --> 06:48.150
Good morning.

07:20.910 --> 07:21.770
It's so hot.

07:35.360 --> 07:37.630
Manager Shen, you look great today.

07:39.650 --> 07:41.240
You're grinning from ear to ear.

07:42.950 --> 07:43.870
The treatment is working well.

07:44.350 --> 07:45.550
Have him continue taking the medicine for a few more days

07:45.570 --> 07:46.740
to clear out the toxins in his body.

07:48.960 --> 07:50.200
Dr. He,

07:50.230 --> 07:51.430
something good happened?

07:51.450 --> 07:52.250
Tell me.

08:14.590 --> 08:16.120
Your papers turned out pretty well this time.

08:16.370 --> 08:17.120
Keep up the good work.

08:17.860 --> 08:18.940
I'll get going now.

08:18.970 --> 08:19.600
Goodbye.

08:23.240 --> 08:25.830
I'd say my paper could use a rewrite.

08:26.280 --> 08:27.520
What's good about it?

08:27.920 --> 08:30.090
Senior He is in an exceptionally good mood today.

08:30.120 --> 08:31.050
Indeed.

08:37.510 --> 08:38.679
Grandpa Yu,

08:38.760 --> 08:41.120
something big happened!

08:45.480 --> 08:46.150
He.

08:46.410 --> 08:47.610
Let's go to the cafeteria.

08:47.670 --> 08:48.790
I'll pass. I'm heading out for a bit.

08:49.610 --> 08:50.480
Alright, take care.

08:54.390 --> 08:55.080
Song Feng.

08:56.820 --> 08:57.470
Good luck.

08:59.830 --> 09:01.540
Good... luck?

09:02.890 --> 09:04.660
Why would I need luck to eat at the cafeteria?

09:33.970 --> 09:36.180
Better confess now, or you'll pay for the bubble tea.

09:38.460 --> 09:39.300
Look at her—

09:40.190 --> 09:43.150
glowing with happiness.

09:45.040 --> 09:46.090
Well,

09:47.280 --> 09:48.360
I'm no longer single.

09:48.380 --> 09:49.320
I have a boyfriend now.

09:52.590 --> 09:53.610
Out of the blue?

09:54.350 --> 09:56.290
I just casually brought it up,

09:56.400 --> 09:57.550
and he said yes.

09:58.810 --> 10:00.690
You brought it up?

10:00.920 --> 10:02.470
So you made the first move?

10:03.400 --> 10:04.620
Nice, you've made progress.

10:05.820 --> 10:07.790
Look at you, all smug.

10:07.810 --> 10:08.880
Don't be so dramatic.

10:09.580 --> 10:12.510
You two were the same back then. So don't judge me.

11:20.620 --> 11:24.510
[Grandpa]

11:24.540 --> 11:25.230
Hello?

11:25.960 --> 11:26.470
Hello.

11:26.850 --> 11:29.210
I heard you're in a great mood today.

11:29.910 --> 11:30.870
Come on, spill.

11:32.470 --> 11:33.640
Li Jie told you?

11:35.000 --> 11:36.360
You and Shen are together now?

11:38.470 --> 11:39.760
When did it happen?

11:40.220 --> 11:41.150
You were so upset

11:41.590 --> 11:43.660
during the Spring Festival.

11:44.430 --> 11:45.950
When did it happen?

11:46.940 --> 11:48.440
Why would I tell you?

11:49.090 --> 11:50.480
You sound so smug.

11:50.500 --> 11:51.530
Listen.

11:51.630 --> 11:53.360
You finally got yourself a girlfriend,

11:53.440 --> 11:54.890
so treat her well.

11:54.920 --> 11:56.350
Don't get too full of yourself.

11:56.370 --> 11:57.560
Cherish her.

11:57.590 --> 11:58.240
Got it?

11:58.240 --> 11:59.270
Got it, got it.

11:59.510 --> 12:00.790
I don't need you to tell me that.

12:01.730 --> 12:02.970
That's it. I'm driving.

12:03.980 --> 12:04.800
Bye-bye.

12:05.390 --> 12:05.960
Bye-bye.

12:18.690 --> 12:19.730
I'm off work.

12:21.300 --> 12:22.460
I'm on my way too.

13:00.680 --> 13:04.150
♫When I see you♫

13:06.000 --> 13:09.360
♫Flowers bloom♫

13:10.350 --> 13:13.920
♫When I see you♫

13:15.670 --> 13:19.350
♫Flowers bloom♫

13:26.480 --> 13:30.420
♫And I don't even know where else to go♫

13:35.050 --> 13:36.120
Dr. He.

13:36.380 --> 13:40.380
♫And I don't even know where else to go♫

13:36.560 --> 13:37.440
He Suye.

13:39.960 --> 13:40.840
Right on time.

13:42.600 --> 13:43.480
Not a minute late.

13:44.010 --> 13:47.820
♫When I see you♫

13:45.210 --> 13:46.090
Wait a second.

13:49.340 --> 13:52.320
♫Flowers bloom♫

13:50.520 --> 13:51.360
What?

13:52.690 --> 13:53.260
Look.

13:55.060 --> 14:02.870
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

13:57.280 --> 13:58.240
You bought it?

14:00.890 --> 14:02.090
I brought you flowers too.

14:04.900 --> 14:11.520
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

14:08.980 --> 14:09.860
You know

14:10.030 --> 14:11.200
that love poem?

14:11.670 --> 14:14.940
"Riding on a red leopard, accompanied by a striped lynx."

14:14.500 --> 14:18.180
♫When I'm with you♫

14:15.140 --> 14:17.570
"With a magnolia-wood carriage and banners adorned with osmanthus."

14:19.290 --> 14:23.200
♫When I'm with you♫

14:20.020 --> 14:22.580
Red leopards and striped lynxes are hard to find,

14:22.820 --> 14:24.630
so I brought you magnolia flowers instead.

14:25.010 --> 14:26.110
There's a poem behind it?

14:26.780 --> 14:31.270
Well, I'm giving you this simply because you like it,

14:31.340 --> 14:32.330
so I want to give it to you.

14:33.490 --> 14:34.170
Thank you.

14:36.380 --> 14:43.440
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

14:38.200 --> 14:39.160
They smell so good.

14:39.200 --> 14:39.790
Do they?

14:40.480 --> 14:41.810
Let's enjoy the fragrance at home.

14:44.880 --> 14:45.500
Let's go.

14:45.770 --> 14:53.130
♫Nothing in this world can take me away from you♫

14:51.320 --> 14:52.290
Where are they going?

14:52.320 --> 14:53.440
To Shen's place, of course.

14:53.460 --> 14:54.850
Look, they're holding hands.

14:55.500 --> 14:59.550
♫When I'm with you♫

14:56.410 --> 14:58.560
What an enviable couple!

15:00.350 --> 15:05.960
♫When I'm with you♫

15:51.580 --> 15:53.460
Do you need any help?

15:54.420 --> 15:55.420
Not here.

15:55.730 --> 15:57.250
Can you scoop some rice out

15:57.360 --> 15:58.400
and set the table for me?

15:58.700 --> 16:00.660
Sure. Is the dinnerware over there?

16:00.680 --> 16:02.320
Everything's there. Be careful.

17:37.170 --> 17:39.480
I made this soup for your granddaughter-in-law. Not bad, right?

17:45.960 --> 17:47.440
Here's the soup.

17:49.520 --> 17:50.690
Thank you.

17:50.800 --> 17:52.880
We're having chestnut chicken soup today.

17:53.020 --> 17:53.690
Looks good.

17:55.330 --> 17:56.000
Try it.

17:56.030 --> 17:56.430
Okay.

17:56.460 --> 17:57.190
Let me ladle some for you.

18:01.770 --> 18:02.400
Try it.

18:12.270 --> 18:12.950
How is it?

18:13.310 --> 18:14.900
It really has a chestnut flavor.

18:14.920 --> 18:15.720
Of course.

18:16.430 --> 18:17.950
I invited you before, but you wouldn't come.

18:29.660 --> 18:30.740
You brat.

18:31.200 --> 18:32.200
It's your first date.

18:32.350 --> 18:34.350
Why didn't you take Shen out for a nice meal?

18:34.690 --> 18:37.090
You should've at least made more dishes.

18:37.200 --> 18:38.370
It's so stingy of you

18:38.400 --> 18:39.850
to just make these few dishes.

18:40.360 --> 18:41.350
Totally unacceptable!

18:42.130 --> 18:44.440
Look, my grandpa is scolding me.

18:44.800 --> 18:45.720
He thinks I'm not treating you

18:45.720 --> 18:46.350
well enough.

18:50.160 --> 18:50.590
Then…

18:51.520 --> 18:52.450
Explain it to him.

18:52.830 --> 18:54.420
You want me to explain?

18:55.640 --> 18:57.270
What am I supposed to say?

18:57.630 --> 18:58.800
Anything. No pressure.

19:00.400 --> 19:00.790
Well,

19:01.480 --> 19:03.160
should I call him Grandpa

19:03.160 --> 19:05.070
or Professor Yu?

19:05.360 --> 19:06.800
Professor Yu will do. Relax.

19:12.810 --> 19:13.930
Professor Yu, hello.

19:13.950 --> 19:15.020
I'm Shen.

19:15.160 --> 19:17.470
I asked He Suye to cook at home

19:17.510 --> 19:19.740
because I think his cooking is amazing,

19:19.840 --> 19:21.600
better than anything from a restaurant.

19:23.330 --> 19:24.280
Take your phone back.

19:24.440 --> 19:25.000
Okay.

19:27.680 --> 19:28.610
You heard that?

19:28.640 --> 19:30.200
My cooking is amazing,

19:30.320 --> 19:31.710
and I treat her very well.

19:38.200 --> 19:39.290
That's just how my grandpa is.

19:40.840 --> 19:41.880
I was so nervous.

19:42.150 --> 19:43.410
What's there to be nervous about?

19:54.500 --> 19:55.500
What did he say?

19:56.740 --> 19:58.310
He feels bad

19:58.330 --> 20:00.570
and thinks he might've left a bad impression on you.

20:00.600 --> 20:02.230
No way. Why would he think that?

20:03.790 --> 20:04.980
That's just how he is—

20:05.000 --> 20:06.200
tough on the outside but soft on the inside.

20:06.230 --> 20:07.550
He's loved roasting me since I was little.

20:08.680 --> 20:11.360
But honestly, he really likes you.

20:12.430 --> 20:13.630
I've only

20:13.650 --> 20:15.560
met him once.

20:15.730 --> 20:17.210
Why does he like me already?

20:17.850 --> 20:18.920
You two met

20:19.000 --> 20:20.090
during your first follow-up visit.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.400
He was covering for me at the clinic.

20:22.190 --> 20:23.590
When he got back, he told me,

20:23.750 --> 20:25.920
"Miss Shen is really pretty."

20:27.740 --> 20:28.540
Why don't you two

20:29.560 --> 20:31.600
have a meal together and get to know each other?

20:37.970 --> 20:39.740
Don't you think it's too soon for me

20:39.810 --> 20:40.720
to meet your family?

20:41.170 --> 20:42.350
It's nothing formal.

20:44.140 --> 20:44.700
Well,

20:45.110 --> 20:46.620
if it's just a casual meal, then sure.

20:46.700 --> 20:47.430
I'm available anytime.

20:48.530 --> 20:50.430
Tell Professor Yu for me

20:50.750 --> 20:52.660
that I really like him too.

20:53.720 --> 20:54.870
What a sweet talker.

20:56.890 --> 20:57.640
No.

20:57.660 --> 20:58.730
I need to reconsider.

20:59.370 --> 21:00.970
If you meet my grandpa like this,

21:01.020 --> 21:02.180
he's going to like you even more.

21:02.200 --> 21:03.650
Then I'll fall out of favor.

21:04.530 --> 21:05.330
I'll spoil you.

21:22.030 --> 21:22.940
What are you watching?

21:23.350 --> 21:24.240
"Twinkling Stars."

21:29.600 --> 21:30.470
Teach me origami.

21:31.310 --> 21:32.200
Origami?

21:33.470 --> 21:35.230
Why are you suddenly interested in that?

21:36.270 --> 21:37.510
I've always wanted to learn it

21:37.540 --> 21:38.870
but never got the chance.

21:40.110 --> 21:40.980
So,

21:41.610 --> 21:42.810
what do you want to make?

21:45.820 --> 21:46.490
A frog,

21:47.130 --> 21:48.480
the kind that jumps when you press it.

21:49.640 --> 21:50.610
Let me tell you.

21:50.640 --> 21:52.470
Making a paper frog is hard.

21:52.490 --> 21:53.580
You need to watch closely.

21:53.950 --> 21:55.920
How hard can it be? Just show me.

21:56.520 --> 21:57.000
Alright.

21:58.780 --> 21:59.690
Look.

21:59.780 --> 22:00.540
Take the paper,

22:00.560 --> 22:01.850
fold it like this,

22:02.230 --> 22:04.430
and then fold it again like this.

22:06.220 --> 22:06.940
Like this.

22:10.250 --> 22:11.340
After that,

22:11.370 --> 22:12.960
unfold the paper

22:14.680 --> 22:16.290
and fold it in half.

22:18.360 --> 22:19.290
Fold it once more.

22:21.370 --> 22:22.170
Like this.

22:22.190 --> 22:23.380
Then…

22:26.350 --> 22:28.160
After folding both sides,

22:28.610 --> 22:30.040
fold these two corners.

22:35.920 --> 22:37.440
Then fold it like this.

22:42.510 --> 22:43.140
Right.

23:03.810 --> 23:05.180
Then like this.

23:16.120 --> 23:17.240
Done.

23:27.590 --> 23:28.510
Someone

23:28.510 --> 23:29.930
was so confident just now,

23:29.960 --> 23:31.960
saying he could definitely get it right,

23:31.980 --> 23:33.500
only to end up with this.

23:33.660 --> 23:35.460
Did you mess up from the very first step?

23:37.110 --> 23:39.260
How could that be?

23:40.110 --> 23:41.790
That's an insult to my intelligence.

23:42.040 --> 23:43.320
That's not what I mean!

23:49.440 --> 23:50.340
He Suye.

23:57.230 --> 23:58.160
Are you angry?

23:59.880 --> 24:00.630
No.

24:03.400 --> 24:04.610
Really?

24:31.600 --> 24:33.560
I just realized something.

24:35.070 --> 24:37.830
Every day I spend with you

24:38.840 --> 24:41.080
makes me incredibly happy.

24:47.680 --> 24:48.570
Alright then.

24:51.030 --> 24:52.350
As long as you're happy,

24:53.560 --> 24:54.840
you can say whatever you want about me.

25:00.630 --> 25:02.560
I was just thinking…

25:04.380 --> 25:06.400
Fortunately, I came to see you yesterday.

25:11.700 --> 25:12.490
I know.

25:14.910 --> 25:17.590
I saw you pacing outside the door.

25:19.350 --> 25:20.470
You saw me?

25:22.180 --> 25:24.220
I saw everything through the peephole.

25:26.480 --> 25:28.330
I was so afraid you'd leave the next second,

25:29.210 --> 25:30.100
but at the same time,

25:30.840 --> 25:32.950
I didn't want to startle you by suddenly opening the door.

25:33.790 --> 25:34.740
So,

25:34.920 --> 25:35.970
I made up an excuse,

25:36.050 --> 25:37.200
saying I needed to take out the trash.

25:39.210 --> 25:41.130
I was afraid that you might reject me

25:41.160 --> 25:42.410
if I said something wrong again.

25:42.440 --> 25:45.170
I wouldn't. Why would I reject you?

25:50.240 --> 25:51.570
Yesterday, you said

25:52.970 --> 25:54.880
you had considered the worst-case scenario—

25:55.150 --> 25:56.790
waiting for me to return from abroad.

26:01.290 --> 26:03.570
But what if, after I come back,

26:05.990 --> 26:07.810
I still haven't figured things out?

26:12.520 --> 26:13.810
Is this a trick question?

26:14.260 --> 26:15.560
I'm being serious.

26:22.380 --> 26:23.730
If one day

26:25.880 --> 26:27.590
you make me feel miserable,

26:29.930 --> 26:31.230
I won't hold onto you anymore.

26:51.310 --> 26:52.350
A relationship

26:53.090 --> 26:54.480
is about two people.

26:56.550 --> 26:57.920
Happiness and joy

26:58.570 --> 26:59.770
should go both ways.

27:02.550 --> 27:03.510
For me

27:03.920 --> 27:04.920
and for you,

27:05.620 --> 27:06.620
it should be the same.

27:08.750 --> 27:09.590
So,

27:11.250 --> 27:12.490
if one day

27:13.650 --> 27:15.540
I make you feel miserable

27:16.770 --> 27:17.810
or

27:18.950 --> 27:20.480
I make you feel unhappy,

27:22.270 --> 27:23.790
you have to tell me.

27:24.970 --> 27:25.940
I'll make changes.

27:29.120 --> 27:30.030
If…

27:31.910 --> 27:33.710
that's still not enough…

27:37.040 --> 27:38.430
you can break up with me.

27:39.350 --> 27:40.480
What are you saying?

27:40.480 --> 27:41.540
Don't say things like that.

27:44.050 --> 27:45.240
I'm saying this

27:45.870 --> 27:47.630
because I truly want you…

27:50.350 --> 27:52.030
to always be happy.

27:56.940 --> 28:02.860
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

28:03.830 --> 28:08.710
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

28:10.560 --> 28:16.480
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

28:17.420 --> 28:22.630
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

28:20.500 --> 28:21.630
He Suye.

28:27.510 --> 28:29.460
Fortunately, I came to see you yesterday.

28:35.920 --> 28:37.780
Fortunately, you came to see me last night.

28:44.340 --> 28:46.690
Fortunately, you opened the door yesterday.

28:50.940 --> 28:52.420
Fortunately, I opened the door.

28:53.450 --> 28:59.370
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

29:00.350 --> 29:05.220
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

29:07.070 --> 29:12.990
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

29:13.930 --> 29:20.640
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

29:32.860 --> 29:39.050
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

29:39.100 --> 29:41.010
I'll tell you the code to my door.

29:41.580 --> 29:42.340
Okay.

29:42.930 --> 29:45.170
112167.

29:46.800 --> 29:48.600
What are those numbers?

29:49.460 --> 29:51.580
It's the ISSN of the English edition of TCM Journal.

29:51.670 --> 29:52.890
My first SCI paper

29:52.920 --> 29:54.070
was published there.

29:55.460 --> 29:56.560
That's so you.

29:58.940 --> 30:00.020
Keep it in mind

30:00.040 --> 30:02.030
so you can open the door yourself when you come.

30:03.200 --> 30:05.120
I'll try my best to remember those numbers.

30:09.070 --> 30:10.920
Actually, if you had left these flowers at my place,

30:11.080 --> 30:12.640
you could still see them every day.

30:13.870 --> 30:15.740
I'll come to see you every day.

30:31.880 --> 30:32.950
A relationship

30:33.710 --> 30:35.270
is about two people.

30:37.130 --> 30:40.330
Happiness and joy should go both ways.

30:50.530 --> 30:52.240
It's such a simple truth.

30:54.150 --> 30:56.350
Why did I not understand it before?

32:03.400 --> 32:04.820
You made it?

32:12.680 --> 32:15.530
I searched for tutorials online. Hard work makes up for clumsiness.

32:20.890 --> 32:23.680
I made that paper frog! Suye threatened me.

32:23.910 --> 32:25.110
He said if I couldn't do it,

32:25.130 --> 32:27.170
he wouldn't help me check the English version of my paper.

32:28.470 --> 32:29.180
Keep it a secret.

32:35.470 --> 32:36.990
Why did you expose him?

32:40.950 --> 32:43.070
I'm too kind.

32:43.090 --> 32:44.930
I couldn't stand to see you get fooled.

33:20.070 --> 33:21.270
What do you need from me?

33:24.280 --> 33:25.610
You got together with that TCM physician?

33:34.320 --> 33:35.190
When?

33:37.620 --> 33:38.630
The night before last.

33:46.170 --> 33:47.070
He's just a lame TCM physician.

33:47.070 --> 33:48.610
What do you see in him?

33:54.930 --> 33:55.730
Yan Heng.

33:56.960 --> 33:58.440
I didn't choose to be with him

33:59.520 --> 34:01.370
because I saw something in him.

34:03.920 --> 34:06.200
I chose him because when I'm with him,

34:06.470 --> 34:07.490
I feel happy

34:07.890 --> 34:08.690
and content.

34:10.100 --> 34:11.580
That's something you could never give me.

34:18.679 --> 34:20.150
Happiness should go both ways.

34:20.800 --> 34:22.030
I wish

34:22.480 --> 34:24.460
you could find the person who makes you happy.

34:33.530 --> 34:35.340
You're checking out today, right?

34:36.020 --> 34:37.550
If you are satisfied

34:37.550 --> 34:38.630
with our service,

34:39.050 --> 34:40.630
we'd love to have you stay with us again.

34:41.179 --> 34:42.500
As the front office manager,

34:42.870 --> 34:44.310
I'll try to offer the best service.

34:50.110 --> 34:51.280
I'll get back to work now.

35:27.290 --> 35:28.330
Goodbye, Mr. Yan.

35:59.430 --> 36:01.150
Please, don't come again.

36:36.950 --> 36:40.850
[Shen Xifan]

36:50.720 --> 36:53.360
What's wrong? Why are you calling me now?

36:59.140 --> 37:00.280
I miss you.

37:06.650 --> 37:08.900
What's wrong? Did something happen?

37:12.890 --> 37:14.090
Nothing.

37:15.230 --> 37:16.670
I just want to tell you

37:18.430 --> 37:19.320
that I miss you.

37:27.100 --> 37:28.370
Thank you for telling me.

37:35.180 --> 37:36.380
I miss you too.

37:58.320 --> 37:59.020
Bye-bye.
